Text: More like a cheap way to get people to listen to some Serbian indie band. Stop spamming. Really.

This is not Lady Gaga. It is Jelena Karleusa, a famous Serbian pop singer. This torrent keeps getting reposted, incorrectly labeled as Gaga with additional fictional credits, such as "produced by P. Diddy" or claims that it is climbing the Euro pop charts. Someone(s) is purposefully reposting this in an attempt to mislead. Check Gaga's wiki, Gagapedia, or the gagadaily site for additional verification of this ongoing fraud.
